## Environment Variables (Standard Rocket Pattern)

### `.env.local`
```bash
# Supabase
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[project-id].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...        # server-side only — never expose

# Stripe
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...           # sk_live_... in production
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...      # pk_live_... in production
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...         # different for test/live/local
STRIPE_PRICE_ID=price_...              # recreate in live mode

# App
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000   # https://your-app.netlify.app in prod

# Email (Resend example)
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
```

